casebody.data:
Cory D. EARLEY, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Stephanie A. VAN HEMERT, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 157964
COA: 341066 Supreme Court of Michigan. October 24, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the May 23, 2018 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
